}
{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
A tenant may not change the lock to the dwelling unit without giving notice to the landlord and giving the landlord a duplicate key within 48 hours of the change. A victim may change the locks to the unit at the victim\rquote s expense. If the victim changes the locks to the unit, the victim shall provide the landlord with a duplicate key within 72 hours of changing the locks. For the purposes of this subsection, \u8220\'3fvictim\u8221\'3f has the same meaning as in section 6000, subsection 4.
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
